  "body": "\nNode types describe what kind of thing a node represents.\n\nThe current canonical registry contains 19 core node types: person, concept, claim, source, essay, observation, media, event, place, organization, project, technology, publication, community, relationship, revision, trail, schema, and fragment.\n",
